in order until it guesses the randomly generated password.

2. Althought we did not implement this in our code, the fastest way to crack the password is likely by using
a more efficient search algorithm like binary search, rather than brute force.


Challenge 2 Questions:
3. It takes longer to crack the password becasue it has to iterate through more numbers.

4.Some strageties people may use to protect there pin numbers are not having common pins
